        <h2>Law Overview</h2>
        <h3>1987 Constitution: Article 13, Section 14</h3>
        <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Promote women's rights and equality in all aspects of life.</p>
        <p><strong>Key Provisions:</strong> Recognizes the importance of women's participation in development.</p>
        <p><strong>Importance:</strong> Establishes a foundation for gender-focused laws and programs.</p>
