        <h3>Example: Application of RA 9262</h3>
        <p><strong>Scenario:</strong> A woman reports domestic violence from her partner.</p>
        <p><strong>Protection:</strong> Grants immediate protection orders, penalizes abusers, and provides victim services.</p>
